decks.notes: This Boros Aggro deck focuses on early aggression and fast damage output, utilizing efficient creatures like Ragavan, Nimble Pilferer and Ocelot Pride. The deck also includes powerful spells like Galvanic Discharge and Goblin Bombardment to control the board and finish off opponents. Ajani, Nacatl Pariah and Phelia, Exuberant Shepherd provide additional support and buff creatures. The deck aims to overwhelm opponents quickly before they can stabilize, utilizing a mix of creatures, spells, and enchantments to maintain pressure and secure victory.
